'''佳能 EOS 450D'''，又称为'''Digital Rebel XSi'''（[[北美|北美]]市场）或'''EOS Kiss Digital X2'''（日本市场）<ref>{{cite_web | url = http://www.dpreview.com/news/0801/08012403canoneos450d.asp | title = Canon EOS 450D / EOS Rebel XSi | date = January 24, 2008 | work = Digital Photography Review | access-date = 2008-06-03 | archive-date = 2011-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111031021709/http://www.dpreview.com/news/0801/08012403canoneos450d.asp | dead-url = no }}</ref>，是由[[佳能公司|佳能公司]]于2008年1月23日推出，3月<ref>{{cite web|title=EOS 450D: get ready to play|url=http://www.canon.co.uk/press_centre/press_releases/cameras_accessories/eos450d_press_release.asp|accessdate=2008-01-24|date=24 January 2008|archive-date=2008-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129090425/http://www.canon.co.uk/press_centre/press_releases/cameras_accessories/eos450d_press_release.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>上市的一款消费级别单镜头反光相机。在北美市场，EOS 450D于同年4月<ref>{{cite web|title=Canon Press Release|url=http://www.usa.canon.com/templatedata/pressrelease/20080123_xsi.html|accessdate=2008-01-24|date=23 January 2008|archive-date=2008-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080223083747/http://www.usa.canon.com/templatedata/pressrelease/20080123_xsi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 上市。作为成功的[[佳能_EOS_400D|佳能 EOS 400D]]的继任者，佳能EOS 450D具有1220万有效像素CMOS图像感应器以及拥有更大的连拍缓存，并且使用3英寸23万像素的宽视角LCD显示屏。

